How shocking. Shocking.

369
00:21:13,487 --> 00:21:17,162
谢谢 大臣 对了 节目录的怎样?
Thank you, Minister. By the way, how did the recording go?

370
00:21:17,367 --> 00:21:21,360
本斯坦利的掩体问题有点麻烦
Well, I got into a bit of bother over Ben Stanley's bunker.

371
00:21:21,527 --> 00:21:25,202
我说政客没有医生重要 之类之类
I said politicians weren't as important as doctors and so on.

372
00:21:25,407 --> 00:21:26,806
是吗?
Did you?

373
00:21:27,387 --> 00:21:28,588
于是他问
Then he said

374
00:21:28,588 --> 00:21:33,279
"首相的政府掩体又怎么说?"
"What about the PM's place in the government shelter?"

375
00:21:32,447 --> 00:21:35,644
