I'm not too sure how happy the PM will be about it.

378
00:21:42,127 --> 00:21:45,722
然后我又想起一件妙事 一群市政委员
Then I recovered with a marvellous story about some councillors

379
00:21:45,887 --> 00:21:48,481
跑到加州去考察掩体
