380
00:21:48,647 --> 00:21:50,676
游山玩水 花掉了
and spent three entire years of

381
00:21:50,676 --> 00:21:54,358
三年的民防预算
the civil defence budget on the jaunt!

382
00:21:56,327 --> 00:22:00,320
