00:22:13,783 --> 00:22:16,959
我大难临头的时候才这么说
when I've made an appalling cock-up.

388
00:22:19,207 --> 00:22:21,281
大臣您知道 那个市里
You do know the borough in question

389
00:22:21,281 --> 00:22:24,599
有首相的选区
contains the PM's constituency...

390
00:22:25,367 --> 00:22:27,437
