10号把消息压了几个星期 不过
Number 10 have been trying to keep it quiet.

394
00:22:40,607 --> 00:22:43,804
算了 纸包不住火啊      别 别
Oh, well, truth will out. No, no, no!

395
00:22:43,967 --> 00:22:49,087
