地方政府衡量指标 这太复杂
failure standards on local councils is very complex.

403
00:23:12,447 --> 00:23:14,722
您要求马上拿出计划
You asked for proposals straight away.

404
00:23:14,887 --> 00:23:17,037
让我一刻也不得闲
It's taking every moment of my time.

405
00:23:17,207 --> 00:23:19,402
要帮忙也有心无力了
Much as I would like to help.

406
00:23:21,367 --> 00:23:24,643
话说回来 如果衡量指标的事
However... if implementing failure standards

407
00:23:24,807 --> 00:23:26,957
不催那么急...
were not quite so urgent...

408
00:23:27,127 --> 00:23:29,800
你是说 你能拦下电视节目?
You mean, you can stop this broadcast?

409
