00:24:47,447 --> 00:24:50,280
尤其是我们的共同市场敌人...
Especially our Common Market enemies...

431
00:24:51,367 --> 00:24:54,245
呃 盟友
...um... partners.

432
00:24:54,407 --> 00:24:56,398
哦 对了
Oh, yes.

433
00:24:56,567 --> 00:24:59,400
针对首相的笑话
Jokes against the Prime Minister.

434
00:24:59,567 --> 00:25:03,242
过分宣传反政府示威
Unnecessary publicly For anti-government demonstrations.

435
00:25:03,447 --> 00:25:07,759
大臣们提出的被拒掉的节目
And ministers' programme suggestions not accepted.

436
00:25:09,447 --> 00:25:12,200
恐怕其它的我包里放不下了
I had no room in my case for the others.

437
00:25:12,367 --> 00:25:15,006
可我们当然对这些都有答复的
I'm sure we have answers to all these.

438
00:25:15,167 --> 00:25:18,159
BBC总有答复 傻不傻另当别论
The BBC's always got answers. Silly ones.

439
00:25:18,327 --> 00:25:21,046
当然 公平起见 我还得警告你
Yes, of course. I thought it fair to warn you

