00:28:37,247 --> 00:28:40,239
不过 我还是有种感觉
Yet, you know, I can't help feeling

503
00:28:40,407 --> 00:28:42,637
有人在陷害我 诱我说出
that I was trapped into saying those things

504
00:28:42,807 --> 00:28:44,877
对首相不利的言论
that might’ve embarrassed the PM.

505
00:28:45,847 --> 00:28:47,883
不会吧?      真的
Surely not? Yes.

506
00:28:48,447 --> 00:28:51,245
我觉得我上了大当了
I think I was dropped right in it.

507
00:28:52,607 --> 00:28:54,677
您怎么能这样胡思乱想?
How could you think such a ridiculous thought?

508
00:28:54,847 --> 00:28:59,079
胡思乱想 汉弗莱? 他不会陷害我吗?
Why is it ridiculous to imagine that he would've tried to trap me?

509
00:28:59,647 --> 00:29:00,921
谁?
Who?

510
00:29:01,607 --> 00:29:03,040
路德维克肯尼迪
Ludovic Kennedy.

511
00:29:04,727 --> 00:29:08,720
哦 路德维克肯尼迪陷害您 那当然
Oh, Ludovic Kennedy tried to trap you. Yes, well, I'm sure he did.

512
00:29:08,887 --> 00:29:11,526
骗子手 一等一级阴险小人 绝对信不过
Deceitful crowd, the medal. Underhand.

513
00:29:11,687 --> 00:29:13,439
对 完全是小人
No, thoroughly deceitful.

514
00:29:13,607 --> 00:29:17,919
对了 我想地方政务委员会的事还是算了
By the way, I think it might be wise to lay off the local councils.

515
00:29:18,087 --> 00:29:19,406
哦 是吗?
Oh, yes?

516
00:29:19,567 --> 00:29:22,415
反正 委员们大体上还是
After all, councillors are responsible,

517
00:29:22,415 --> 00:29:25,164
讲道理又负责的
sensible people on the whole.

518
00:29:24,327 --> 00:29:27,319
而且是民主选举出的      民主选举
And they are democratically elected. Democratically elected.

519
00:29:27,487 --> 00:29:30,001
说真的 中央政府必须万分小心
Central government must be frightfully careful

520
00:29:30,167 --> 00:29:32,476
不能越权给他们乱下指示
before it tells them how to do their jobs.

521
00:29:32,647 --> 00:29:36,720
万分小心 衡量指标的事呢?
Frightfully careful. And the failure standards?

522
00:29:36,887 --> 00:29:41,085
我看也是一个道理 你说呢?
Well, I think the same applies... don't you?

523
00:29:41,247 --> 00:29:42,839
是 大臣
Yes, Minister.

